name: IG#712 – glitch in the stream of time
description: This work transforms the phenomenon of the different human realities of life that exist simultaneously in parallel, moving in the stream of time.  The original video footage was recorded by the artist in India 2014. The glitches are programmed by the artist with MaxMSP. Video 1080x1080p, 35sec, by Michel Winterberg 2021, https://michelwinterberg.ch
